lead_paragraph: The ecstasy of Danny Willett's three-shot victory at the Masters on Sunday will forever be linked to the eye-popping agony of Jordan Spieth's stunning collapse on the back nine at Augusta National.

headline.main: Can Spieth Rebound From Agony of Masters Meltdown?
